  ('medical-tech-moex-20041', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-094-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關口服抗凝血劑Coumarin藥效之實驗室監測，以下列何者最合適？ 以部分凝血活 時間（Activated partial thromboplastin time）作為監測 以凝血 時間（Thrombin time）監測 以國際敏感性指數（International sensitivity index）監測 以國際正常化比值（International normalized ratio）監測', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:14+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "96d440809c0b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "bc22c58d926f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "105", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 50, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-20042', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-094-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '急性免疫性血小板缺乏紫斑症（Autoimmune thrombocytopenic purpura）病人之出血時間（Bleeding time）延 長，是因為： 血小板醣蛋白受體被抗體結合   自體免疫影響凝血因子活性   血小板數目減少   發 生血液凝固活化而消耗血小板', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:14+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "96d440809c0b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "bc22c58d926f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "105", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 51, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-20043', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-094-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', 'Fibrin degradation products（FDP）之FPA及FPB是在那個步驟形成？ Plasmin 切割Fibrin時    Thrombin切割Fibrinogen時 Prothrombin活化成thrombin時  第十因子活化時', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:14+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "96d440809c0b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "bc22c58d926f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "105", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 52, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
